<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-684] ConsoleProducer does not have the queue-size option</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-684</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using the kafka ConsoleProducer (from script kafka-console-producer.sh), you cannot set the queue.size, which gets very annoying when  you want to produce quickly a lot of messages. You definitely need to increase the queue.size (or decrease the send timeout).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is a simple patch to add the option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
