                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13546291" author="junrao" created="Mon, 7 Jan 2013 21:37:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch. It looks good. While you are here, could you also expose the following properties (from SyncProducerConfig) in ConsoleProducer?&lt;br/&gt;
producer.request.timeout.ms&lt;br/&gt;
producer.request.required.acks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13546728" author="brugidou" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2013 09:30:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;queue.enqueueTimeout.ms&lt;br/&gt;
producer.request.required.acks&lt;br/&gt;
producer.request.timeout.ms&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13546746" author="brugidou" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2013 10:07:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While I&apos;m at it, I added this small feature:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Exit at end of input stream (so you can do echo &quot;test&quot; | ./kafka-console-producer.sh or ./kafka-console-producer.sh &amp;lt; test without stopping the producer manually&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13547329" author="junrao" created="Tue, 8 Jan 2013 21:57:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for patch v3. +1. Committed to 0.8.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
